{"prompt": "Generate a website for a real estate brokerage. The website should be dynamic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Redstone Realty</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #c0392b;\n            --secondary-color: #e74c3c;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            --dark-text: #34495e;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background: #ffffff;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            background: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--brand-color);\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .property-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .property-card {\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background: #fff;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .property-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n\n        .property-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n\n        .property-info {\n            padding: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .property-info h3 {\n            margin: 0 0 10px 0;\n            color: var(--dark-text);\n        }\n\n        .property-info p {\n            margin: 5px 0;\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n        }\n\n        .property-info .price {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            transition: background 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--secondary-color), var(--brand-color));\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--dark-text);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.7), rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x600/c0392b/ffffff?text=Beautiful+Homes') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            height: 400px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .hero .cta-button {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .hero .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Redstone Realty</h1>\n        <p>Your Partner in Finding Your Dream Home</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#properties\">Properties</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Discover Your Next Chapter</h2>\n        <p>Find exceptional homes in your favorite neighborhoods.</p>\n        <a href=\"#properties\" class=\"cta-button\">View Listings</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"properties\">\n            <h2>Featured Properties</h2>\n            <div class=\"property-grid\">\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e74c3c/ffffff?text=Luxury+Condo\" alt=\"Luxury Condo\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Stunning City Condo</h3>\n                        <p>3 Beds | 2 Baths | 1800 sq ft</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$750,000</p>\n                        <p>Modern living in the heart of downtown.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/c0392b/ffffff?text=Family+Home\" alt=\"Family Home\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Charming Family Home</h3>\n                        <p>4 Beds | 3 Baths | 2500 sq ft</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$620,000</p>\n                        <p>Spacious backyard, perfect for families.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e74c3c/ffffff?text=Beach+House\" alt=\"Beach House\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Seaside Retreat</h3>\n                        <p>3 Beds | 2.5 Baths | 2100 sq ft</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$950,000</p>\n                        <p>Ocean views and private beach access.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/c0392b/ffffff?text=Modern+Townhouse\" alt=\"Modern Townhouse\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Sleek Urban Townhouse</h3>\n                        <p>2 Beds | 2.5 Baths | 1500 sq ft</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$580,000</p>\n                        <p>Contemporary design with rooftop terrace.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Redstone Realty</h2>\n            <p>Redstone Realty is a premier real estate brokerage dedicated to providing exceptional service and expertise to our clients. We are passionate about real estate and committed to helping you navigate the market with confidence. Whether you're buying your first home, selling a beloved property, or searching for an investment opportunity, our team of experienced agents is here to guide you every step of the way.</p>\n            <p>Our deep understanding of the local market, combined with our innovative marketing strategies, ensures that your real estate goals are met with efficiency and success. We believe in building lasting relationships based on trust, integrity, and personalized attention.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <p>Have questions or ready to find your dream home? Contact us today!</p>\n            <form class=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <input type=\"tel\" placeholder=\"Your Phone Number\">\n                <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Redstone Realty. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple JavaScript for potential future enhancements\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}